    "description": "> MEDIUM CONFIDENCE! | Genome-wide epistasis and co-selection study using mutual information | SpydrPick is a command line tool for performing 'direct coupling analysis' of aligned categorical datasets. It constructs a coupling graph based on thresholded node-pair Mutual Information (MI) scoring, followed by pruning of edges that represent indirect couplings using the ARACNE algorithm | Mutual information based detection of pairs of genomic loci co-evolving under a shared selective pressure | Home: https://github.com/santeripuranen/SpydrPick | License: GNU Affero General Public License",
